import { Stack, Typography, Avatar } from "@mui/material";

//---------------------------------------------

export default function MarmaraUniversity() {
  return (
    <Stack mb={2} mt={2}>
      <Stack
        direction="row"
        alignItems="flex-end"
        mb={2}
        justifyContent="flex-start"
        flexDirection="row-reverse"
      >
        <Avatar
          alt="Marmara University"
          src="./img/logo/marmara-universitesi.jpeg"
          sx={{ width: 56, height: 56 }}
          variant="rounded"
        />
        <Stack direction="column" alignItems="flex-end" pr={2} pl={2}>
          <Stack direction="row" spacing={1}>
            <Typography variant="caption" color="white" gutterBottom>
              January 2021 - July 2022
            </Typography>
          </Stack>
          <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
            Marmara University
          </Typography>
        </Stack>
      </Stack>
      <Stack direction="column" alignItems="flex-end">
        <Typography variant="caption" gutterBottom>
          Worked on Microsoft Azure App Platform
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="caption" gutterBottom>
          Used GitHub and Git distributed version control system
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="caption" gutterBottom>
          Pipeline supervision check is done
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="caption" gutterBottom>
          New dashboard are developed with React js
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="caption" gutterBottom>
          In .NET developed with DDD architecture and CQRS Designed Database
          Structure
        </Typography>
      </Stack>
    </Stack>
  );
}
